# Utils

## StringUtils

### capitalize(string: string): string

Capitalizes the first letter of the input string and returns the modified string.

### reverse(string: string): string

Reverses the input string and returns the modified string.

## ArrayUtils

### isEmpty(array: any[]): boolean

Checks if the input array is empty and returns a boolean value indicating the result.

### flatten(array: any[]): any[]

Flattens the input array and returns a new array with all the elements flattened.

## DateUtils

### format(date: Date, format: string): string

Formats the input date according to the specified format and returns the formatted string.

### addDays(date: Date, days: number): Date

Adds the specified number of days to the input date and returns the modified date.
